  <brief_title>Negative Pleural Suction for Tube Thoracostomy in Patients With Chest Trauma</brief_title>
  <official_title>Efficacy of Negative Pleural Suction in Tube Thoracostomy for Patients With Penetrating and/or Blunt Chest Trauma: a Randomized Clinical Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
